    19тЖТ
    20тЖТ**mdBook** is a command line tool to create books with Markdown.
    21тЖТIt is ideal for creating product or API documentation, tutorials, course materials or anything that requires a clean,
    22тЖТeasily navigable and customizable presentation.
    23тЖТ
    24тЖТ* Lightweight [Markdown] syntax helps you focus more on your content
    25тЖТ* Integrated [search] support
      тЖТтАж
    46тЖТ## Contributing
    47тЖТ
    48тЖТmdBook is free and open source. You can find the source code on
    49тЖТ[GitHub](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook) and issues and feature requests can be posted on
    50тЖТthe [GitHub issue tracker](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/issues). mdBook relies on the community to fix bugs and
    51тЖТadd features: if you'd like to contribute, please read
    52тЖТthe [CONTRIBUTING](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) guide and consider opening
    53тЖТa [pull request](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/pulls).
    54тЖТ
